All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ApproveSuggestionInterface
The ApproveSuggestionInterface provides methods for viewing camp suggestions and approving a suggestion.
Camp
Represents a camp with various attributes such as name, dates, location, and attendees.
CampApp
The main class for the Camp Application And Management System.
CampCommitteeMember
Represents a committee member extending the Student class with additional committee-related functionalities.
CampDBManager
Manages the camp database by providing methods to convert, retrieve, create, delete, and save camp information.
CampFilter
Provides methods for filtering and sorting camps based on various criteria.
CampManager
Manages camps, including reading from and writing to CSV files, creating, editing, and deleting camps.
CampPrinter
Provides methods for printing information about camps, including their names, descriptions, locations, dates, and availability.
CampUserInterface
Interface for handling user authentication within the camp management system.
CSVReader
This class provides basic functionality for reading and manipulating CSV files.
DateStr
Utility class for converting between Date and String representations in the "dd/MM/yyyy" format.
Enquiry
Represents an enquiry made by a student for a specific camp, along with the associated replies.
EnquiryDBManager
Manages the storage and retrieval of enquiries and their replies in the CSV file.
EnquiryInterface
An interface defining methods for managing enquiries.
EnquiryManager
The EnquiryManager class manages user inquiries and replies, interacting with CSV data.
EnquiryReply
The EnquiryReply class represents a reply to an enquiry.
EnquiryReplyInterface
The EnquiryReplyInterface provides methods for viewing camp enquiries and replying to an enquiry.
InputHandler
The InputHandler class provides methods for handling user choices based on their roles in the Camp Application and Management System.
MenuHandler
The MenuHandler class provides methods for displaying and handling user menus based on their roles (Student, Staff).
PointsSystem
The PointsSystem class provides methods for managing and retrieving points for users in the system.
ReportGenerator
The ReportGenerator class provides methods for generating performance reports for camps.
Staff
The class represents a staff member involved in managing camps.
Student
The Student class represents a user with the role of a student in the system.
Suggestion
Represents an Suggestion made by a commitee member, and its data.
SuggestionDBManager
Manages the storage and retrieval of suggestions in the CSV file.
SuggestionInterface
The SuggestionInterface interface defines methods for managing suggestions.
SuggestionManager
The SuggestionManager class manages suggestions from commitee members, interacting with CSV data.
User
The User class represents a user in the Camp Application and Management System.
UserDBManager
Manages the storage and retrieval of user information from CSV files.
UserInterface
The UserInterface represents the interface for user-related operations in the system.
UserManager
The UserManager class manages user-related operations in the Camp Application and Management System.
